Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.44,0:00:07.06,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Song by Rina Aiuchi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.44,0:00:07.06,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Koi wa thrill, shock, suspense
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.73,0:00:07.11,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,Koi wa Thrill, Shock, Suspense,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.36,0:00:10.74,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,Mienai chikara tayori ni
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.86,0:00:18.33,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,Kokoro no tobira tozasazu ni tsuyoku... tsuyoku...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.66,0:00:22.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A brave heart and incredible deductions,\Na rhythm that jumps to the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.33,0:00:24.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a unique mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.92,0:00:26.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A prosperous business leads to a case!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.08,0:00:28.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seeing the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.54,0:00:30.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A kid with the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.55,0:00:32.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is... Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.38,0:00:36.30,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,Watashi ga kanjiteita
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.88,0:00:47.03,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,Toge okimi ni no onaji You ni ataeteita no kano shirenakatta
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.13,0:00:53.47,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,Nani ni kokoro o itamete nani ni obieteita no ka
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.60,0:00:58.04,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,Ki ni ino tomezu motsureteku futari no shinjitsu ni
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.17,0:01:01.45,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,Mukiau no ga kowakatta
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.44,0:01:06.92,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,This love is Thrill, Shock, Suspense,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.08,0:01:14.22,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,Mayoi o aoi kaze ni chirasou toshite Mo kakaekirezu ni ita yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.32,0:01:17.72,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,Kono chisana mune ni wa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.82,0:01:21.26,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,Kokoro no tobira tozasazu ni
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.43,0:01:25.83,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,Tsugi e to susumu arata na fuan to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.93,0:01:35.34,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,Mayoi o kakaeteshimaisou ni natte mo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.37,0:01:46.91,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,The Secret of the High Sales
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.58,0:01:50.54,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Teitan Primary School
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.88,0:01:54.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A suspicious man?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.55,0:01:55.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.67,0:01:59.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doesn't your family own a restaurant?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.89,0:02:02.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know that restaurant! It's the Manpuku!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.72,0:02:03.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.43,0:02:10.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's dark and dirty, and the food is disgusting,\Nso the place is always empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.27,0:02:12.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.02,0:02:14.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, why do you think that man is suspicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.23,0:02:18.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because, two months ago, he appeared out of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.28,0:02:25.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello, my name is Kamekura Yuuji. I owe a favor\Nto the deceased owner and I'd like to repay him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.41,0:02:24.79,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Kamekura Yuuji (28)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.87,0:02:27.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To my deceased husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.00,0:02:29.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What kind of favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.62,0:02:32.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I owe him something so important\Nthat I can't express it with words.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.71,0:02:39.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, to demonstrate my enormous gratitude,\NI would like to stay here and work for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.22,0:02:43.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You want to live with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.26,0:02:46.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-But we don't have the money to hire another worker.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.27,0:02:49.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not asking to be paid!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.31,0:02:51.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just want to return the favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.44,0:02:54.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please let me stay and work for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.23,0:02:56.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's get to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.78,0:03:01.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And so, he invited himself to live with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.07,0:03:09.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think there is something wrong, because my grandfather\Nwho died was selfish and had a bad personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.37,0:03:12.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that he never did a favor for anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.75,0:03:15.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that that man is after something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.67,0:03:19.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I want the Detective Boys to discover what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.34,0:03:21.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.68,0:03:27.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought it would be an interesting case, but it's only\Na liar that has intruded into someone's home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.31,0:03:31.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think that he is planning a crime!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.64,0:03:33.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I say the same thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.06,0:03:33.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.98,0:03:37.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everything about it sounds {\i1}really{\i0} suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.73,0:03:39.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haibara...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.69,0:03:43.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right! The time has come for the Detective Boys to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.20,0:03:43.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.49,0:03:46.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good luck, Edogawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.58,0:03:49.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I would really like to go, but I have other things to attend to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.29,0:03:50.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bye bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.75,0:03:53.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't leave us Haibara!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.42,0:03:55.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.46,0:03:58.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.63,0:04:01.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the Manpuku restaurant?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.01,0:04:02.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.09,0:04:04.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the restaurant is clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.64,0:04:07.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And look at how many people are waiting to enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.10,0:04:12.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all because of that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.07,0:04:21.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We haven't had any customers today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.44,0:04:23.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, there is nobody around, like always.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.74,0:04:28.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, there are a lot of clean restaurants\Nwith delicious food out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.20,0:04:33.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.21,0:04:37.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.08,0:04:39.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since I have a lot of experience as a chef,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.50,0:04:44.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am going to teach you guys how to cook and redecorate\Nthe shop so that it attracts more customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.76,0:04:46.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Redecorate it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.22,0:04:50.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I will pay for all of it, so don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.72,0:04:52.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just want to repay him for when he helped me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.93,0:04:53.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.81,0:05:00.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ever since then, the restaurant has been doing great.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.52,0:05:06.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's suspicious about him using his own money to\Nredecorate the restaurant to show his gratitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.61,0:05:08.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems like he's a very grateful man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.82,0:05:09.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.83,0:05:14.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He wants to make the business boom and\Nthen run off with the profit, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.87,0:05:17.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you think that's what he's planning?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.12,0:05:21.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's what he wanted, then why is he helping you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.21,0:05:24.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't it be faster to just find a profitable\Nrestaurant in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.84,0:05:26.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.18,0:05:29.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez... A crime? What a stupid idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.51,0:05:32.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.56,0:05:33.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.48,0:05:38.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I am thinking of a new menu. Please\Ndo not disturb. Kamekura."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.60,0:05:44.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, he has been in his room day and\Nnight creating a new menu for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.57,0:05:50.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He won't let us enter because he says\Nhe wants to keep his menu a secret—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.24,0:05:52.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rintaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.37,0:05:56.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have a lot of work to do. Since\Nyou are here, give us a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.33,0:05:58.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, say goodbye to your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.33,0:06:01.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.59,0:06:04.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the shop has a lot of work,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.76,0:06:07.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the family will spend most of its time working.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.13,0:06:14.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,During that time, he's in his room doing something secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.22,0:06:18.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This, without a doubt, reminds\Nme of The Red-Headed League!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.14,0:06:20.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.27,0:06:22.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.40,0:06:25.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Guys, I am sure this is the same as The Red-Headed League.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.44,0:06:28.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, The Red-Headed League!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.36,0:06:30.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.70,0:06:38.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Red-Headed League is one of the 60 famous\Ncases that Sherlock Holmes investigated.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.58,0:06:44.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A man worked for a store as an employee, and convinced\Nthe owner to leave by finding him another job.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.75,0:06:51.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While the owner was working, he dug an underground\Ntunnel to rob the bank next door.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.84,0:06:55.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a grand and very daring crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.93,0:06:58.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the complete explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.44,0:07:03.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, I would like to add that it was\Nwritten more than 100 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.44,0:07:08.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I doubt that there is a thief nowadays that has the\Npatience to dig a tunnel to steal something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.11,0:07:13.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you guys doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.95,0:07:16.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he's digging a tunnel, we should be able to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.20,0:07:20.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be so foolish!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.83,0:07:22.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll prove it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.33,0:07:24.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prove it, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.01,0:07:34.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.05,0:07:34.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.93,0:07:37.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's going on, Rintaro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.56,0:07:39.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.02,0:07:41.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mister, sorry to bother you while you're busy,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.64,0:07:45.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but you're like a god of good fortune!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.02,0:07:47.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ever since you've arrived, the restaurant\Nhas been doing great!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.44,0:07:50.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you show me your hands, I'll check your good fortune line.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.74,0:07:52.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.65,0:07:53.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.99,0:07:56.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at them however long you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.03,0:07:57.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-Those are...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.20,0:08:00.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.46,0:08:07.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hey, what did his good fortune line say?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.55,0:08:10.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wasn't looking at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.30,0:08:13.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There were a lot of blisters and calluses on his hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.72,0:08:16.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're hands that have been using a shovel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.10,0:08:20.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's hard to believe, but he is digging a hole under the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.85,0:08:23.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you so, I knew I was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.81,0:08:25.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Amazing, Mitsuhiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.61,0:08:30.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mitsuhiko figured it out this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.15,0:08:34.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could something like this seriously be happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.66,0:08:38.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, we need to find where he's digging a tunnel to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.66,0:08:40.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.58,0:08:49.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I get it now. The nearest bank to the\NManpuku restaurant is on this side.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.80,0:08:52.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, it's closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.55,0:08:55.97,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Closed
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.92,0:08:56.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been closed for more than a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.84,0:08:58.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can't be his objective.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.35,0:09:03.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were wrong, it looks like you've failed again, Conan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.06,0:09:09.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, the place the thief is interested in has to be closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.57,0:09:12.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, there's a jewelry store!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.15,0:09:19.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's impossible for our jewelry store to be robbed, kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.45,0:09:25.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After a previous incident, we installed a\Nsecurity system that can't be breached.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.96,0:09:28.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A bad experience?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.33,0:09:31.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right, little lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.46,0:09:34.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One day, a thief stole 3 million yen worth of jewels.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:37.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The truth is, the thief hasn't been captured yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.34,0:09:42.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A jewel thief, and he hasn't been captured?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.76,0:09:44.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then it is possible that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.68,0:09:48.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you tell us when those jewels were stolen?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.23,0:09:50.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well this coming month would make five years.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.32,0:09:53.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then I don't think...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.57,0:09:58.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A jewel thief, and a suspicious man\Ndigging a tunnel underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.53,0:10:00.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I understand now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.03,0:10:02.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mitsuhiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.41,0:10:03.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mitsuhiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.83,0:10:07.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey Mitsuhiko, don't tell me you're thinking {\i1}that{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.21,0:10:12.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Mitsuhiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.67,0:10:15.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have to go, I'm very busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.01,0:10:16.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.92,0:10:19.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did you ask her, Mitsuhiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.59,0:10:22.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've solved the case!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.76,0:10:30.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The man named Kamekura is, without a doubt, the\Nthief that robbed the jewelry store five years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.56,0:10:32.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's the jewel thief?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.23,0:10:32.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.52,0:10:35.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am convinced that my hypothesis is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.74,0:10:41.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I also thought the same thing, but that\Ndeduction has many dark spots.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.28,0:10:45.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, this thief is not stupid at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.04,0:10:51.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he sold all the jewels at once, he would\Nhave been found out and captured.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.21,0:10:57.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was also risky to keep the jewels during\Nall of those years, so he buried them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.96,0:11:02.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He probably buried them under Rintaro's house,\Nas it was being reconstructed at that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.97,0:11:05.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How did you know that the house was being reconstructed?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.77,0:11:09.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that what you were asking the woman earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.98,0:11:11.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.19,0:11:16.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kamekura came into their house as a worker\Nso that he could dig little by little,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.48,0:11:19.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and in this simple way recover all his stolen jewels.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.40,0:11:21.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're incredible, Mitsuhiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.41,0:11:23.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a perfect deduction, amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.07,0:11:26.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, come on. It wasn't much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.49,0:11:29.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're amazing. Even though I thought the same thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.16,0:11:32.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did he wait for five years?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.67,0:11:36.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You still don't get it, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.38,0:11:41.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's pretty obvious that he was waiting until\Nthe five year crime expiration ran out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.84,0:11:47.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, pretty soon he can dig them up and\Nsell them all without a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.85,0:11:52.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You are correct in that the prosecution\Nfor a criminal case is five years.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.98,0:11:57.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, the expiration period of a civil crime is 20 years.\NEven if he gets the jewels now, they won't belong to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.69,0:12:02.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We don't know the laws by heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.49,0:12:06.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we didnt know that detail, surely\Nthe thief doesn't know either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.16,0:12:09.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.04,0:12:12.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You just have to argue about everything,\Ndon't you Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.17,0:12:19.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My mother always tells me that sometimes it's better\Nto just accept things without arguing back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.92,0:12:22.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not the problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.42,0:12:27.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go to the police right away and tell them that\Nhe's the jewel thief that they're looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.14,0:12:27.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.64,0:12:30.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We don't have proof. You're going to humiliate yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.85,0:12:36.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's fine, all we have to do is catch him red handed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.15,0:12:37.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How are you going to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.86,0:12:39.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We will lay a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.61,0:12:43.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A trap? Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.04,0:12:58.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's you guys again. Do you want\Nto see the palm of my hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.30,0:13:02.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We came to tell you that we know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.51,0:13:04.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh, what did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.59,0:13:08.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't easily trick the Detective Boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.55,0:13:09.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.60,0:13:12.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.27,0:13:16.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.23,0:13:23.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now the only thing we have to do is\Nwait for him to fall into our trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.49,0:13:26.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And what is supposed to happen now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.36,0:13:30.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He is going to panic, make a mistake, and we'll discover it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.37,0:13:31.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.20,0:13:32.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.29,0:13:37.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How is it possible for an adult to be scared by\Na threat from a bunch of primary school kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.38,0:13:40.75,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,The Next Morning
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.25,0:13:44.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? The whole family is going\Nto a hot spring this weekend?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.76,0:13:49.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, that man recommended to my father that we should go,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.43,0:13:57.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,because we haven't rested a day since\Nthe reopening of the restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.19,0:14:00.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And of course, that man isn't going.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.77,0:14:04.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he says only family members should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.78,0:14:09.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This way he can get everybody to\Nleave, so he can finish digging.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.87,0:14:11.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course. That must be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.78,0:14:16.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you, Conan! He fell into our trap and is hurrying to dig.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.79,0:14:18.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.08,0:14:20.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this really happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.59,0:14:29.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't have the slightest idea of what's happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.84,0:14:32.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seems like this case is confusing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.01,0:14:39.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, why would a criminal panic over\Na few words said by some kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.52,0:14:42.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's unbelievable! There are a bunch\Nof things that don't make any sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.61,0:14:43.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kudo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.86,0:14:51.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe you are confused because this criminal doesn't do\Nthe same things as the criminals you usually handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.57,0:14:53.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.78,0:14:55.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He is a very simple person.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.79,0:14:59.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm even more confused now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.04,0:15:05.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} has lost his confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.84,0:15:08.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, this time he's really depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.01,0:15:12.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hope he doesn't rebel and become a juvenile delinquent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.76,0:15:14.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That could happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.55,0:15:17.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't like it if that happened to a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.48,0:15:23.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you don't want to come with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.69,0:15:27.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I have a friend that lives around here\Nand I already made plans with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.61,0:15:29.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, have a good time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.40,0:15:36.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What luck! Before we couldn't even\Nafford to have a day of rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.16,0:15:40.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And thanks to Kamekura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, the restaurant is doing great!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.33,0:15:44.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're lucky that such a good man came to our home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.59,0:15:47.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like everyone just left.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.80,0:15:51.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now to wait for Kamekura to return home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.13,0:15:55.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you going to wait all night? What if he doesn't show up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.10,0:15:57.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are we going to tell our parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.56,0:15:59.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, there he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.69,0:16:13.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now all we have to do is get into the restaurant with the\Nkey that Rintaro left us, and catch him red handed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.03,0:16:14.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.87,0:16:18.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you alright, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.13,0:16:32.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've been digging for days and still haven't found anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.30,0:16:36.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't have buried them too deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.72,0:16:39.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.22,0:16:41.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I found them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.44,0:16:47.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I found them! The jewels, the jewels, my precious treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.99,0:16:56.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.08,0:17:03.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We now know that you buried the jewels.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.17,0:17:08.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.00,0:17:13.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, we aren't the police, so we can't arrest you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.05,0:17:14.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.84,0:17:16.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go where? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.51,0:17:21.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, what else? Aren't you going to\Ntell the criminal your deductions?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.77,0:17:24.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We left the best part for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.68,0:17:28.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because you haven't done much this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.10,0:17:30.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, I have nothing to say to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.57,0:17:32.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.11,0:17:33.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good luck, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.03,0:17:40.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kamekura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, five years ago you entered a jewelry\Nstore and stole three million yen's worth of jewels.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.41,0:17:42.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't contradict me, I know what I say is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.62,0:17:44.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well yeah, that's what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.58,0:17:47.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you just admitted your crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.96,0:17:50.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, I'm not an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.59,0:17:53.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know that, if I sold them, the police would locate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.21,0:18:01.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, I saw that this house was being reconstructed,\Nburied the jewels underground, and ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.60,0:18:06.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I then worked day after day so the\Npolice wouldn't suspect me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.73,0:18:08.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had to bear everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.98,0:18:12.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Such as being screamed at and hit by my boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.98,0:18:16.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even my friends stopped working as apprentices\Nbecause they couldn't stand him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.90,0:18:18.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Except for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.11,0:18:23.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I believed that, in five years, those jewels would be mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.74,0:18:30.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what inspired me to keep going,\Nno matter what would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.08,0:18:34.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And finally, after five years, the time has come!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.30,0:18:36.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't wait for the crime expiration date to pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.05,0:18:39.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wanted to dig right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.55,0:18:44.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why you invented a story to work\Nhere and start digging up the jewels.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.47,0:18:50.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it wasn't easy, since there weren't any customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.81,0:18:53.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The family members were always sitting around the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.27,0:18:57.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was no chance for you to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.32,0:19:03.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, you decided to spend your own\Nsavings to renovate this restaurant,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.45,0:19:06.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and teach them some cooking skills that you've learned.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.87,0:19:09.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thus, making the business prosper.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.29,0:19:14.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You made it so the entire family was in the\Nrestaurant and kept busy the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.00,0:19:20.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This way, you could start your work\Ndigging and looking for the jewels.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.93,0:19:24.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Kamekura Yuuji{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.93,0:19:27.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's exactly how it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.02,0:19:31.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We hit the bulls eye. We're awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.35,0:19:34.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's one thing I don't understand though.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.52,0:19:39.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did you start panicking? Just because some primary\Nschool kids told you that they knew everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.99,0:19:45.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because I'm such a coward. I even got scared\Nafter hearing the words "Detective Boys".
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.33,0:19:49.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.83,0:19:53.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's impossible for a normal adult to be afraid just because\Na bunch of little kids say a bunch of nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.83,0:19:59.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you just send all of them\Nto the hot spring from the start?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.59,0:20:03.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It would have been easier, cheaper, and faster,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.68,0:20:11.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,if you gave them a free trip instead of wasting that money,\Nreforming the restaurant, and waiting for it to prosper.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.98,0:20:13.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What an absurd plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.56,0:20:15.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.69,0:20:17.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.90,0:20:21.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess that does make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.03,0:20:22.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you do that then?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.53,0:20:25.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hadn't thought of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.58,0:20:30.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This case is closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.04,0:20:31.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haibara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.91,0:20:33.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Convinced?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.67,0:20:34.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haibara.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.38,0:20:40.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you before that this man was way simpler\Nthan the other criminals you have encountered?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.93,0:20:46.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're already here, I called them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.43,0:20:51.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Incredible! Maybe we'll be rewarded by the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.31,0:20:53.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That would be great!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.14,0:20:54.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.73,0:20:58.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure they will. After all, you guys did a great job.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.19,0:21:00.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You think that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.86,0:21:02.32,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Yes, without a doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.86,0:21:02.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I suppose we did.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.74,0:21:12.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hate this. Even after solving the case, I feel horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.00,0:21:17.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hate this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.84,0:21:22.84,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Start in my Life
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.84,0:21:22.84,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Song by: Mai Kuraki
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.09,0:21:29.68,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,ii koto bakari no mirai janai keredo
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.09,0:21:29.68,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,The future will bring misfortune, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.43,0:21:45.19,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,tashika ni ima wa ashita ni mukai dare yori mo kagayaki
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.43,0:21:45.19,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,I will continue running to tomorrow, brightly shining.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.11,0:22:01.88,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,koko ni tatteiru koware kake souna ima ni namidashi soredemo
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.11,0:22:01.88,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,Now, standing here, shedding tears for the weak... Even...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.13,0:22:08.01,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,We can start in my life issho ni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.13,0:22:08.01,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,We can start in my life together...
