Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.26,0:22:12.26,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,And follow our dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.22,0:22:24.36,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,nee mou hitori no jibun ni aeru kara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.22,0:22:24.36,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,You can even meet your other self.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.86,0:22:31.82,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,kimochi hitotsu de kawarerun da
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.86,0:22:31.82,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,With one feeling, we can change.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.83,0:22:37.41,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,hora koko kara hajime you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.83,0:22:37.41,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,Let's start here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.16,0:22:42.75,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,Just start in my life
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.16,0:22:42.75,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,Just start in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.05,0:22:52.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We received a letter of thanks for helping in the jewel\Nthief's arrest before the case's expiration period.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.01,0:22:56.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.02,0:22:59.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was so easy this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.56,0:23:02.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, I need to say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.73,0:23:06.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know that most criminals aren't as idiotic as this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.49,0:23:12.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So don't let your guard down because of this.\NIt was dangerous to follow him like we did.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.49,0:23:16.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? What's wrong with you, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?\NYou have been very jittery lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.62,0:23:22.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You must've felt humiliated since we\Nstole your thunder, right Conan?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.04,0:23:26.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}? Don't you see that\NConan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} is sulking cause of what's happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.17,0:23:30.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cheer up, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}. It doesn't really matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.76,0:23:33.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry, Conan. It's really nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.26,0:23:35.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You idiots...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.60,0:23:38.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My intelligence should be used in\Nsolving complex criminal cases,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.22,0:23:41.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,where our brains engage in a spectacular battle of wits.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.02,0:23:43.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't really care about these minor cases at all!
